Here we dedicated to bulding the important core infrastrucure components inside the market participant's trading system. First, we build the market data consumer component, which is responsible for subscribing to the multicast market data stream generated by the exchange. 
It needs to detect gaps in market data updats on the incremental market data stream and initiate snapshot recovery and synchronization mechanisms to re-synchronize with the incremental market data stream. 
It decodes the market data updates from the format that the exchange publishes to a simpler internal market data format 

